            <span class="px-3 py-1.5 border border-border text-xs font-medium text-text-muted">ICF PCC Certified</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1.5 border border-border text-xs font-medium text-text-muted">Former CHRO</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1.5 border border-border text-xs font-medium text-text-muted">Published Author</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1.5 border border-border text-xs font-medium text-text-muted">Keynote Speaker</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5 text-lg">
            With over 25 years of global and Indian experience as a former CHRO and Chief Learning Officer, I've sat on both sides of the table.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-lg">
            I know what organisations look for in the leaders they back — and I know exactly what gets in the way.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Portrait -->
