        <div class="lg:col-span-4 fade-in">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-gold mb-4">The Story</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary leading-tight">A career built in the boardroom. A practice built on clarity.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-8 fade-in">
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-lg">
            With over 25 years of global and Indian experience as a former CHRO and Chief Learning Officer, I've sat on both sides of the table. I know what organisations look for in the leaders they back — and I know exactly what gets in the way.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Over two decades at P&amp;G, GE, and Genpact, I led global teams of 1,000+ people across eight countries and five continents. I've seen what separates the leaders who rise from the ones who stall — and it's rarely about capability.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Since founding RYSEN Coaching, I've partnered with organisations like Google, PayPal, DHL, and IKEA — helping their most talented leaders find the clarity to step fully into what comes next.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-lg">
            The most rewarding feedback I receive from clients is simple: <em class="text-text-primary font-medium not-italic">&ldquo;You helped me find myself again.&rdquo;</em>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHILOSOPHY CARDS -->
  <section class="bg-bg border-t border-border py-24 lg:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-in mb-16">
